oracle.mapviewer.share
Class GeoRasterBitmapMask

java.lang.Object
  oracle.mapviewer.share.GeoRasterBitmapMask

public class GeoRasterBitmapMask
extends java.lang.Object

From Database 11 each GeoRaster record may have binary image masks. This class defines a bitmap image mask that can be associate with a GeoRaster theme. The parameters are: rasterid: raster identifier; rdtname: raster data table name; layers: mask layers array; zeromapping: mapping value (0-255) for pixel 0. Mapping value close to 0 means more transparency; onemapping: mapping value (0-255) for pixel 1. Mapping value close to 0 means more transparency.
